提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 00:23:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/scientists-create-artificial-neurons-that-help-cure-chronic-diseases</guid></item><item><title>人造塑料神经元展示出先进的类脑功能</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/artificial-plastic-neurons-demonstrate-advanced-brain-like-functions</link><description>瑞典林雪平大学的研究人员展示了一种由导电塑料制成的人工神经元，可以执行类似于生物神经细胞的高级功能。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/artificial-plastic-neurons-demonstrate-advanced-brain-like-functions2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 00:08:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/artificial-plastic-neurons-demonstrate-advanced-brain-like-functions</guid></item><item><title>修复大脑的人工神经元 — Google 搜索</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/artificial-neurons-to-repair-the-brain-google-search</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Jul 2026 23:53:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/artificial-neurons-to-repair-the-brain-google-search</guid></item><item><title>人工智能时代的大脑植入</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/brain-implants-in-the-age-of-artificial-intelligence</link><description>虽然 RNS 和 DBS 是市场上具有标签用途和标签外用途的脑植入物，但还有一类脑植入设备纯粹处于临床研究领域。这些脑机接口使用微电极记录细胞水平数据，并允许机器学习算法控制计算机光标和机械臂。博士的开创性工作首次在非人类灵长类动物中证明了此类设备的功效。道恩·泰勒、安德鲁·斯瓦茨和同事。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/brain-implants-in-the-age-of-artificial-intelligence.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Jul 2026 23:38:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/brain-implants-in-the-age-of-artificial-intelligence</guid></item></channel></rss>